        {
            "title": "奶茶股狂飆10%，年內近乎翻倍！Warren AI亮\"估值紅燈\"",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nxPpFXPmPXGhujCjzaDxTQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC4H0HF_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，4月30日，奶茶股滬上阿姨 (HK:2589)盤中大升10%，年內股價接近翻倍！</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"590\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/B6HHscrjmXtN.OEXVPX1tQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/2e3e885fa5b810e0fae94b999c6f55b8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Warren AI分析指出，滬上阿姨已進入「高增長-高估值-高波動」三高階段，短線仍有交易機會，但需防範高位回撤風險。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>消息面：業績與擴張雙輪驅動</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>2025</strong><strong>年營收同比增長</strong><strong>36%</strong><strong>至</strong><strong>44.66</strong><strong>億人民幣，淨利潤同比大增</strong><strong>52.4%</strong><strong>至</strong><strong>5.01</strong><strong>億人民幣。</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">門店總數達11,449家，較上年增長24.8%，已突破1萬家大關，反映門店擴張持續強勁。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">券商預測2026-2028年淨利將分別達6.7/7.8/9.0億人民幣，維持「買入」評級，2026年給予15倍PE，並測算合理價值108.28港元/股。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滬上阿姨印尼首店落地雅加達高端商圈 Emporium Pluit Mall，開業人氣火爆，前三日日均銷量近1500杯。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>技術面：極端強勢，風險同步抬升</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>近期單日升幅超</strong><strong>12%</strong><strong>，年內累計升幅接近翻倍，技術形態處於加速上升階段。</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">短線成交量急劇放大，主力資金活躍，動能極強。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但已出現多次大陽線拉升，短期技術指標臨近超買，波動性顯著提升。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以「放量突破」、「平台整理後加速」為典型結構，後續需關注資金面持續性。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>估值分析：估值高位，風險升溫</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2026年預測PE為15倍，券商給予目標價空間約23%（由88.2港元至108.28港元）。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當前P/E達22.0x，PEG 0.79，遠高於行業均值，回撤風險突出。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">需警惕擴張放緩、單店收益波動等潛在風險因素，滬上阿姨2025年關閉門店1,383家，閉店率12.11%，為同業最高。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">券商對滬上阿姨的看法存在明顯分歧，看多派以銀河證券、廣發證券為代表，核心邏輯是多品牌矩陣加速擴張疊加咖啡+早餐場景增量；海通國際則下調至\"中性\"，直指閉店率高企及補貼退坡風險。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>5</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月最新</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股即將上線！依家訂閱</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>，<span>唔好錯過啦！</span></span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"480\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/c8btmIWRGCFYTTfPcn2L3g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/55c306ced78e7aede67eacacd53f9e49\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p></blockquote></div>",
